com.oneops.proxy.keywhiz.http

Interface HttpStatus


  • public interface HttpStatus
    Constants enumerating the HTTP status codes. All status codes defined in RFC1945 (HTTP/1.0), RFC2616 (HTTP/1.1), RFC2518 (WebDAV) and RFC7540 (HTTP/2) are listed.
    Since:
    4.0
    See Also:
    RFC1945 (HTTP/1.0), RFC2616 (HTTP/1.1), RFC2518 (WebDAV), RFC7540 (HTTP/2)
